<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/128900067-callum-wilson"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/128900067-callum-wilson">Callum Wilson</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Off the top of my head I would recommend &quot;The Little Shadows&quot; by Marina Endicott (Vaudeville), and &quot;Painted Devil&quot; by Michael Bedard (puppet shows). &quot;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Off the top of my head I would recommend "The Little Shadows" by Marina Endicott (Vaudeville), and "Painted Devil" by Michael Bedard (puppet shows). "Shadows" is more a more mature, realist novel but "Devil" is fun read and introduction to the magical world of Bedard.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
