        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer968921975" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8965361411178867256">Everything Angela Carter wrote was interesting, but for me, this last novel was her best. Full of humour and imagination, this Gothic theatrical tale is a book I must read again some day.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


