<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28501482-the-invention-of-angela-carter"><img alt="The Invention of Angela Carter: A Biography" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1466343851l/28501482._SX98_.jpg" />
